originalText.text: Katya is a super talented photographer who produces beautiful photos! I really felt that she invested in my photoshoot, the preparation for it, and in every photo itself, and I appreciated it so much. It’s clear that Katya cares deeply about getting the very best photos for her clients. She is also there to offer help with wardrobe choices, hair and makeup. Katya is a kind and warm person who is fun to work with, and she is truly an expert in what she does - she helps you feel at ease during the photoshoot and makes it an empowering experience that you won’t forget!

originalText.text: The photoshoot with Katya was an amazing experience. Katya started preparing me starting 2 weeks before with almost daily suggestions on wardrobe and accessories. During the shoot she made me feel very comfortable and guided me step-by-step. I never liked being photographed before, but Katya showed me how to access a side of me I did not know existed. The pictures came out beyond my most optimistic expectations! I can highly recommend Katya and plan to go back for another session.

originalText.text: Finally made the investment to get some professional headshots and was thrilled to have the chance to work with Katya! I went for the whole package and it was well worth it. Prior to the shoot, Katya provided prep guidelines and helped me choose outfits, accessories, etc. and then on the day of the shoot did my hair & make-up so I would like my very best in the photos -- and I did! Katya worked with me until I felt very comfortable posing & trying on different looks and we had a lot of fun doing it. Love all the final shots. Highly recommend Katya!!

originalText.text:
Absolutely Fabulous!

Katya is a super energetic, charismatic, talented and gifted photographer! I had my best photo shoot ever; I felt blessed by her instruction, appreciation for what looks good on camera and skill as a photographer. I've had many fails in this area, spending thousands of dollars on poor pictures. These experiences left me feeling unattractive and not photogenic. Katya has a very special touch--she won't let 50 shots go by if your hair or makeup is off. If the clothing isn't working, she'll help to fix it on the spot...anything to get the right shot, one that makes you look your best.

She's definitely a special kind of lady! If you want a photographer that will take her time to ensure you love your photos no matter what, Katya is the one!

originalText.text:
I am not comfortable in front of the camera.  I needed some photos and an acquaintance recommended Katya. We met before we took photos to get to know each other.  After seeing me, Katya made suggestions on clothes ( styles, color etc).

Meeting and communicating with Katya before the photo shoot gave me the comfort that I needed to be myself during the shoot.  Katya knows how to make you feel good during the shoot.  Katya captured my spirit....not just the physical me.

The photos of me are beautiful.  I am very happy with them and will use Katya again and recommend her highly.
